{{Quote|Even on the run, you might have heard of our wedding. They said a billion men had their hearts broken when Wynssa Starflare wed. I know of one man who felt made whole in that same ceremony.|Soontir Fel|<ref name="SWG">[[X-Wing Rogue Squadron 25|''X-Wing Rogue Squadron'' 25]]</ref>}}
The '''wedding of Soontir Fel and Wynssa Starflare''' was a high profile event which took place [[1 ABY/Legends|one year after the Battle of Yavin]]. While members of [[Soontir Fel/Legends|Fel's]] [[Fel dynasty|family]] attended the wedding, [[Syal Antilles Fel|Starflare's]] brother, [[Wedge Antilles/Legends|Wedge Antilles]], was notably absent.

The famous couple followed up the wedding with a two-week honeymoon planned by Starflare on an exotic [[Unidentified world (Soontir Fel)|world]], the name of which Fel never learned.

